# plus the no-session-resurrection fix (PM-Labs/mcp-google-ads b2b6a33..246ac3d),
# which is incompatible with upstream's approach. Keep ours.
#
# The standalone non-merge commits contributing to the OAuth change and related
# packaging/lint noise that we also don't want:

3e0d25c  upstream OAuth proxy implementation — we have our own + session-resurrection fix
958f8b8  MANIFEST.in .txt addition — we build via docker, not pypi
45f609d  README-only update for upstream OAuth docs — not relevant to our fork
de051e6  upstream lint pass — noise, not worth the conflict surface
